These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, sailing, swimming
House: tower, palace, cape-cod, victorian
1. the victorian house is not to the right of the tower house##8
2. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
5. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the victorian house##8
6. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the palace house##7
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the victorian house have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who's sport is sailing and the tower house have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | cycling | ice-hockey | sailing     | swimming |
| Pet           | cape-cod   | victorian     | palace | tower  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, havana, baccarat, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, handball, ice-hockey, rowing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing and the havana-smoker have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
4. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
6. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
7. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
8. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | bolivar     | baccarat    | aristoff | havana    |
| Hobby      | skiing | handball | ice-hockey      | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, classical, funk, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5
3. the fan classical is on the left of the fan funk##1
4. the fan classical is on the far left##1
5. the fan rock is on the right of the fan funk##1
6. the fan funk is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
8. the fan classical and the owner of the ferret have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | classical    | funk   | rock    | hip-hop  |
| Food       | ferret | chinchilla | fish | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, blend, havana
4 different pets are kept: horse, goat, mouse, snake
1. the owner of the horse is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
4. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the havana-smoker and the owner of the snake have the same parity positions##9
7. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | havana | blend | bluemaster  | oliveros |
| Music-Genre   | mouse             | goat          | snake | horse    |

