.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, dancing, woodworking
House: palace, craftsman, tower, farmhouse
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the tower house##6
2. the palace house and the person who's hobby is reading have different parity positions##9
3. the craftsman house and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing have different parity positions##9
4. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
5. the palace house is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the craftsman house##6
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
8. the palace house is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
9. the farmhouse house is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | reading | dancing | woodworking  | rock-climbing |
| Pet           | craftsman   | palace     | tower | farmhouse      |

