2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
4. the person traveling to rome and the person eating kiwi have the same parity positions##9
5. the person eating grapefruit and the person traveling to rome have different parity positions##9
6. the person traveling to boston is not to the left of the person eating cabbage##8
7. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
8. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | lime | cabbage | kiwi | grapefruit |
| Nationality   | hannover        | boston    | rome   | nizza |

