.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, december, august
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, french, russian, turkish
1. the turkish is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
2. the person who's birthday is in august and the turkish have the same parity positions##9
3. the french is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the french##3
5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the french and the turkish##7
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | december | september   | february | august |
| Transport   | russian   | french | nigerian    | turkish      |

