.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, reggae, d&b, country
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, july, november
1. the fan country is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
2. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the fan d&b is not to the left of the fan country##8
4. the fan country is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
5. the fan country is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan d&b##1
8. the fan gospel is the person who's birthday is in january##1
9. the fan country and the person who's birthday is in february have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | reggae   | country    | d&b | gospel    |
| Nationality   | november | february | july   | january |

