2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
5. the person watching western movies is the person traveling to rome##1
6. the person watching horror movies and the person traveling to berlin have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food          | liverpool | colone | rome   | berlin   |
| Nationality   | crime       | horror | western | superhero |

