4. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
8. the colonial house and the person who's birthday is in june have the same parity positions##9
9. the gothic-revival house and the person who's birthday is in november have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
