.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, apricot, yellow, white
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, animation, drama, spy
 1. the person who likes apricot and the person watching drama movies have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the person who likes apricot##8
 3. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes green##7
 4. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 5. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person who likes white##8
 7. the person who likes white and the person watching animation movies have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 9. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | green  | white | yellow  | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | spy | drama     | documentary | animation     |

