.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, boat, helicopter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, disaster, action, family
1. the person driving the helicopter and the person watching western movies have the same parity positions##9
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
4. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
5. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
6. the person watching action movies and the person driving the trike have the same parity positions##9
7. the person watching western movies and the person driving the boat have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | trike | helicopter | motorbike | boat |
| Pet   | action    | disaster   | family        | western            |

