4. the person eating peas and the person driving the ship have the same parity positions##9
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating peas##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
