.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There 4 different types of food: carrotmelon, lettuce, cherry, carrot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, musical, action
 1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 3. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 4. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person eating lettuce##6
 6. the person eating carrot is not to the right of the person eating carrotmelon##8
 7. the person eating carrot and the person watching horror movies have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
 9. the person eating carrot is the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person eating lettuce and the person watching horror movies have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | lettuce    | cherry        | carrot   | carrotmelon      |
| Hobby      | action | musical | horror | fantasy |

 